title: Wrangler Women's High Rise Bold Boot Jean
description: HIGH RISE BOOTCUT. As the most recognized and celebrated fit in the Wrangler portfolio, this time-tested favorite has a flattering boot-cut silhouette and a higher rise in the back for added coverage.
TIMELESS STYLE. Make a statement in high-quality boot cut jeans inspired by the western lifestyle. Express your true, authentic self through timeless pieces by Wrangler.

FASHION FOR ALL. Available in sizes 0-18, these jeans are made to be loved by every body. Designed with an ageless mindset and authentic fabric with the perfect amount of stretch to make all body types feel confident.

EVERYDAY STAPLE. Designed for women on the go, these high-waisted boot cut jeans deliver an effortless, classic look to any ensemble. Pair with your favorite top and accessories for a polished outfit.

ICONIC FINISHES. This jean is finished with our iconic "W" stitching, leather Wrangler patch, logo shanks and flat rivets. Maintain that effortless classic style with a touch of Wrangler heritage. Inseam: short 30", regular 32", long 34". Zipper fly.

Look no further than Wrangler for authentic, on-trend looks you'll feel good in. We took our most timeless styles and elevated them to fit the modern woman. Available in sizes 0 to 18, or XS to XXL, and made with the perfect amount of stretch, our styles are made to flatter every body. From tailored skinny jeans to fashionable denim jackets, complete your outfit with authentic statement pieces that express your true self.
